      "path": "/books/al-kafi:2:4:21:9",
      "relations": null,
      "text": [
        " رَأَيْتُ أَبَا عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) يَجْلِسُ فِي بَيْتِهِ عِنْدَ بَابِ بَيْتِهِ قُبَالَةَ الْكَعْبَةِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from hammad Bin Usman who said, ",
          "‘I saw Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> sit in his<sup>asws</sup> house by the door of his house, facing the Qiblah’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "9. Ali has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘Umayr from Hammad ibn ‘Uthman who has said the following: “Once, I saw abu ‘Abd Allah (a.s.) sitting in his house near the door facing the Ka’bah.” "
        ]
      }
